<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" size="6" color="#000066">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" size="4" color="#ff6600"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="6" color="#c0c0c0"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"></font></div><span lang="en-GB"><div style="margin: 0px;"><font face="Calibri,sans-serif" size="2" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><font color="#002060" size="3"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></font></span></font><font face="Arial,Sans-Serif" color="#000000" size="3"><div style="margin: 0px;">As a school we take the issue of air pollution very seriously and are investigating different solutions to ensure the wellbeing of our students and staff.</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">We are looking at both stand-alone in-class solutions and solutions that will work with our air conditioning system. We want to be sure that we select the most reliable and efficient solution. We have been testing various stand-alone in-class solutions over the last weeks. Currently, a leading supplier of air purifiers has installed six machines across the school and are taking twice daily measurements of PM2.5 and PM0.3 and comparing these measurements with the same data from locations without an air purifier.&nbsp;</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">Before these trials were put in place we took measurements across the school. We were encouraged to see that our existing air conditioning systems dramatically improves the air quality. On average, the PM2.5 measures are reduced by between 50% and 70% inside classrooms.</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><br></div><div style="margin: 0px;">We hope to have all the information on the table to take a decision shortly and will inform you of that.</div><br>Warm Regards,</font></div><div style="margin: 0px;"><font color="#000000" face="Arial, sans-serif"><div style="margin: 0px;">Janet Brock</div><div style="margin: 0px;"><b>Headteacher</b></div></font></div></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; "><br></p></div></span></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; "><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
